      <title>沙特香水制造商计划通过 IPO 融资高达 1.88 亿美元</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-25/saudi-perfume-maker-aims-to-raise-up-to-188-million-in-ipo</link>
